{
  "name": "Active Camouflage",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "modules/pf1spheres/assets/icons/spheres/scout.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Whenever you move at least 10 ft. in a round and begin and end your turn in cover or concealment, you gain a competence bonus to Stealth checks equal to 1/2 your ranks in Stealth (minimum 1) for one round. You must end your movement in a different square than the one you started your turn to receive this benefit. If you use the Sniper function of the Stealth skill, the penalty to Stealth checks is reduced by -10 (to a minimum of 0).</p>\n",
